     O                         S2SRT 3 +  0
     O                         S2SRTX  +  0
     O                         P2PRC   +  2
     O                         S2AF  3 +  2
     O                         S2AFX   +  0
     O                                 +  3 '('
     O                         S2IN  3 +  2
     O                         S2INX   +  0
     O                                 +  0 ')'
     O                         S2BF  3 +  4
     O                         S2BFX   +  0
